{"tid":732503,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"泰洞被困少年原來係英撚 心願見證三獅世盃封王","createTime":"2018-07-07T03:42:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-11T20:57:08.000Z","uid":66260,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"482360dc7cf5bca4f26d614f1edd5d4425907831","tid":732503,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T03:42:18.000Z","msg":"泰國少年足球隊13人至今仍被困洞穴10多日，其中一名13歳少年Sompong Jaiwong，從上星期拍下的相片見到他正穿上英格蘭球衣。Pong是英格蘭和利物浦的球迷，希望看見英格蘭能夠贏得世盃冠軍，還想有朝一日可以踢英超。<br />\n<br />\nPong的叔叔對傳媒表示:「我們非常擔心他，只想他平安回家。他平時會和我一起看世界盃，他很想英格蘭贏。」他的夢想是成為一名足球員，代表國家隊出賽。叔叔還透露，他最喜歡美斯，但亦愛英國足球和哈利卡尼。<br />\n<br />\n三獅隊守將史東斯和隊友都有留意泰國少年隊的情況，史東斯說：「我們對他們現在身處的情況感到難過，希望他們可以安然無恙地回家。雖然他們現在聽不到我們的說話，但這是說給他們的朋友﹑家人和所有球迷，我們的精神與他們一起。」<br />\n<br />\n國際足球協會亦向泰國足球協會發出慰問信，以表達深切的慰問和支持。國際足球協會主席恩芬天奴還在信中指，如果他們能平安出來而身體狀況許可的話，想邀請他們來俄羅斯看世界盃決賽。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180706/large/1530882891_3f85.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180706%2Flarge%2F1530882891_3f85.jpg&h=ee34c20b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n少年Sompong Jaiwong撐英格蘭"},{"pid":"ec7898da773d924d82f2b4fed7b6b189c448b9ce","tid":732503,"uid":66260,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T03:43:41.000Z","msg":"利物浦教頭高普用球會口號替被困者打氣：你們永遠不會獨行<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180706/s00005/4d943e95c5e31dc41e30b55f440d95f6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180706%2Fs00005%2F4d943e95c5e31dc41e30b55f440d95f6.jpg&h=e9a77146&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n泰國當局及各國救援隊伍，正爭分奪秒營救被困北部清萊府洞穴的12名青少年足球隊員及其教練。英超球會利物浦教練高普接受CNN訪問時，特地拍片為一眾受困者打氣，並引用著名口號「你們永遠不會獨行」（You&rsquo;ll never walk alone），呼籲他們不要放棄。<br />\n<br />\n高普指：「所有利物浦大家庭的成員都會從心底裏支持你們，我們每一秒都希望你們可以重見天日，所以你們要堅強下去，你們永遠不會獨行！」"},{"pid":"b04471913e2f727ae060028d6b66635a3b1b42ce","tid":732503,"uid":79562,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T03:44:19.000Z","msg":"到佢死個日都見唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ee35c044acd20ef8c3949af4bb21d1f94f0864b","tid":732503,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b04471913e2f727ae060028d6b66635a3b1b42ce","tid":732503,"uid":79562,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T03:44:19.000Z","msg":"到佢死個日都見唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T03:44:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1c8aa45722fdb09fbb517662896029ddd116d9e","tid":732503,"uid":66260,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"b04471913e2f727ae060028d6b66635a3b1b42ce","tid":732503,"uid":79562,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T03:44:19.000Z","msg":"到佢死個日都見唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T03:45:59.000Z","msg":"俾D信念佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n應該話佢可以生存到英撚奪冠果日"},{"pid":"9bfc46db9655c51f9c3fafcf0d3400fe9d81565d","tid":732503,"uid":3244,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T04:00:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"296cc324cfb598892083878ca26eac2b3f29f2e6","tid":732503,"uid":154385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T04:00:13.000Z","msg":"you&rdquo;ll never walk alone <br />\n自己咒自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35798a5ff7cf93f6b318d8912e0c735c194e9cb3","tid":732503,"uid":43041,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a1c8aa45722fdb09fbb517662896029ddd116d9e","tid":732503,"uid":66260,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"b04471913e2f727ae060028d6b66635a3b1b42ce","tid":732503,"uid":79562,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T03:44:19.000Z","msg":"到佢死個日都見唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/ba